Container and Truck drivers have taken over the Apapa Oshodi-Express road, as the e-call up system, an initiative of the Lagos state government, seems to have failed to address the lingering heavy traffic situation that as continued to cripple economic and social activities of the area.    Vanguard News Nigeria   All rights reserved. This material and any other digital content on this platform may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, written or distributed in full or in part, without written permission from VANGUARD NEWS.